Ideas for ScorpioFS
--------------------
* symmetric encrypted metadata
* serialize metadata file if in lowmem mode
* chunk popularity for metadata file (load to memory the most popular chunk)
* fetch random chunks for metadata
* collaboration--filesharing (groups, permissions etc)
* traffic information--report (seeders, leechers, files, chunks)
* trustable peers 
* anonymity (I2P)
* disk quota
